1953000.effect: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand or GY) by banishing 3 other face-up "D.D." cards in your possession. You can only use each of the following effects of "D.D.T.A. - Tech Ataxas" once per turn. ● (Quick Effect): You can target up to 3 monsters your opponent controls; banish them and this card until the End Phase. ● During the End Phase: You can reveal this card in your hand; send 1 "D.D." card from your Deck to your GY.
1953000.name: D.D.T.A. - Tech Ataxas

1953006.effect: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand or GY) by banishing 3 other face-up "D.D." cards in your possession. Your opponent cannot activate the effects of banished cards. Banish any monster destroyed by battle with a "D.D." monster you control. You can only use each of the following effects of "D.D.T.H. - Tech Hwatah" once per turn. ● If this card destroys a monster by battle: You can banish 1 card from your GY; this card can attack an opponent's monster again in a row, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent, but any battle damage your opponent takes from this card is halved for the rest of this turn. ● During the End Phase: You can reveal this card in your hand; add 1 "D.D." card from your GY to your hand.
1953006.name: D.D.T.H. - Tech Hwatah

1953010.effect: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand or GY) by banishing 3 other face-up "D.D." cards in your possession. Unaffected by your opponent's card effects that do not target it. This card can attack while in face-up Defense Position. If it does, apply its DEF for damage calculation. This card can attack directly, but when it does so using this effect, the battle damage inflicted to your opponent becomes 2000. You can only use each of the following effects of "D.D.T.Z. - Tech Zymuk" once per turn. ● If this card inflicts battle damage to your opponent: You can banish the top 8 cards of their Deck, face-down. ● During the End Phase: You can reveal this card in your hand; return 1 of your banished "D.D." cards to the GY.
1953010.name: D.D.T.Z. - Tech Zymuk

Insurgence". You can only activate 1 "D.D. Insurgence" per turn.
